<lb ed="T" n="0779a25"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說盂蘭盆經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0779a26" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0779a27"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0779005" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔西〕－【宋】</note><note n="0779005" type="mod" resp="CBETA">西【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0779005"><lem wit="【大】">西</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>晉<note type="orig" n="0779006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779006" type="mod">月氏三藏【大】，三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779006"><lem wit="【大】">月氏三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0779a28" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT16p0779a2801">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0779a2804">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。大
<lb n="0779a29" ed="T"/>目<note type="orig" n="0779007" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">乾＝犍【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779007" type="mod">乾【大】，犍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779007"><lem wit="【大】">乾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">犍</rdg></app>連始得六通，欲度父母，報乳哺之恩。即
<pb n="0779b" ed="T" xml:id="T16.0685.0779b"/>
<lb n="0779b01" ed="T"/>以道眼觀視世間，見其亡母生餓鬼中，不見
<lb n="0779b02" ed="T"/>飲食，皮骨連<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779008" type="orig">立＝柱【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779008" type="mod">立【大】，柱【宮】</note><app n="0779008"><lem wit="【大】">立</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">柱</rdg></app>。目連悲哀，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779009" type="orig">即＋（以）【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0779009" resp="CBETA">即【大】，即以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779009"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">即以</rdg></app>鉢盛飯，往餉
<lb n="0779b03" ed="T"/>其母。母得鉢飯，便以左手障<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779010" type="orig">飯＝鉢【三】</note><note n="0779010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">飯【大】，鉢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779010"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">鉢</rdg></app>，右手摶<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779011" type="orig">飯＝食【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0779011" resp="CBETA">飯【大】，食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779011"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="T" n="0779b04"/>食未入口，化成火炭，遂不得食。目連大叫，悲
<lb ed="T" n="0779b05"/>號<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0779012">啼＝涕【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0779012" resp="CBETA">啼【大】，涕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779012"><lem wit="【大】">啼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">涕</rdg></app>泣，馳還白佛，具陳如此。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0779b06"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779b0601">佛言：「汝母罪根深結，非汝一人力所奈何！汝
<lb n="0779b07" ed="T"/>雖孝順，聲動天地，天神、地<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0779013">神＝祈【宋】，祇【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779013" type="mod">神【大】，祈【宋】，祇【元】【明】</note><app n="0779013"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">祈</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">祇</rdg></app>、邪魔、外道、道
<lb ed="T" n="0779b08"/>士、四天王神亦不能奈何！當須十方眾僧威
<lb ed="T" n="0779b09"/>神之力乃得解脫。
<lb ed="T" n="0779b10"/>吾今當<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779014" type="orig">〔為汝〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779014" type="mod" resp="CBETA">為汝【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779014"><lem wit="【大】">為汝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>說救濟之法，令一切難皆離憂
<lb n="0779b11" ed="T"/>苦，<note n="0779015" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔罪障消除〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779015" type="mod" resp="CBETA">罪障消除【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779015"><lem wit="【大】">罪障消除</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0779b12"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779b1201">佛告目<note n="0779b1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">連【CB】【麗-CB】，蓮【大】</note><app n="0779b1201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">連<note type="cf1">K11n0277_p0621a18</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">蓮</rdg></app>：「十方眾僧<note type="orig" n="0779016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779016">於【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779016"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七月十五日僧自恣
<lb n="0779b13" ed="T"/>時，當為七世父母及現在父母厄難中者，具
<lb n="0779b14" ed="T"/>飯、百味五果、汲灌盆器、香油<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779017" type="orig">錠爥＝挻燭【宋】，鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779017">錠爥【大】，挻燭【宋】，鋋燭【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779017"><lem wit="【大】">錠爥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">挻燭</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">鋋燭</rdg></app>、床敷臥具，
<lb ed="T" n="0779b15"/>盡世甘美以著盆中，供養十方大德眾僧。當
<lb n="0779b16" ed="T"/>此之日，一切聖眾或在山間禪定、<note n="0779018" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔或〕－【宮】</note><note n="0779018" type="mod" resp="CBETA">或【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0779018"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得四道
<lb ed="T" n="0779b17"/>果、<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0779019">或＋（在）【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779019">或【大】，或在【元】【明】</note><app n="0779019"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">或在</rdg></app>樹下經行；或六通自在、教化聲聞、緣
<lb n="0779b18" ed="T"/>覺；或十地菩薩大人權現比丘，在大眾中；皆
<lb n="0779b19" ed="T"/>同一心，受鉢和羅飯。具清淨戒聖眾之道，其
<lb n="0779b20" ed="T"/>德汪洋，其有供養此等自恣僧者，現<note n="0779020" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">在＝世【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779020">在【大】，世【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779020"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世</rdg></app>父
<lb ed="T" n="0779b21"/>母、<note n="0779021" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><note n="0779021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">七世父母【大】，〔－〕【元】【明】</note><app n="0779021"><lem wit="【大】">七世父母</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779022" type="orig">六種親屬＝六親眷屬【三】</note><note n="0779022" type="mod" resp="CBETA">六種親屬【大】，六親眷屬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779022"><lem wit="【大】">六種親屬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">六親眷屬</rdg></app>得出三途之苦，應
<lb n="0779b22" ed="T"/>時解脫，衣食自然。若<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779023">〔復有人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779023" type="mod">復有人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779023"><lem wit="【大】">復有人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>父母現在者，福
<lb n="0779b23" ed="T"/>樂百年；若<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779024" type="orig">〔已亡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">已亡【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779024"><lem wit="【大】">已亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七世父母，生天，自在化生，入
<lb n="0779b24" ed="T"/>天華光，<note type="orig" n="0779025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔受無量快樂〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779025" type="mod" resp="CBETA">受無量快樂【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779025"><lem wit="【大】">受無量快樂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」時佛勅十方眾僧，皆
<lb ed="T" n="0779b25"/><note n="0779026" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔先〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="0779026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">先【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0779026"><lem wit="【大】">先</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>為施主<note n="0779027" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔家〕－【宮】</note><note n="0779027" type="mod" resp="CBETA">家【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0779027"><lem wit="【大】">家</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>呪願<note n="0779028" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">（願）＋七【三】</note><note n="0779028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">七【大】，願七【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779028"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">願七</rdg></app>世父母，行禪定意，然
<lb n="0779b26" ed="T"/>後受食。初受<note n="0779029" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">盆＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779029" type="mod" resp="CBETA">盆【大】，食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779029"><lem wit="【大】">盆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">食</rdg></app>時，先安在佛<note type="orig" n="0779030" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">塔＝前塔寺中佛【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779030" type="mod">塔【大】，前塔寺中佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779030"><lem wit="【大】">塔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前塔寺中佛</rdg></app>前，眾僧呪
<lb ed="T" n="0779b27"/>願竟，便自受食。</p>
<lb n="0779b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779b2801"><note n="0779031" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔爾〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779031" type="mod">爾【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0779031"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時目連比丘及<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779032">〔此大會〕－【三】，此大會＝此大眾【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0779032" resp="CBETA">此大會【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】，此大眾【宮】</note><app n="0779032"><lem wit="【大】">此大會</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">此大眾</rdg></app>大菩薩眾皆大
<lb ed="T" n="0779b29"/>歡喜，<note n="0779033" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔而〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779033" type="mod">而【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779033"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>目連悲啼泣聲釋然除滅。<note n="0779034" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔是〕－【元】</note><note n="0779034" type="mod" resp="CBETA">是【大】，〔－〕【元】</note><app n="0779034"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時目
<pb xml:id="T16.0685.0779c" n="0779c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0779c01" ed="T"/>連<note n="0779035" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779035">其【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779035"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>母即於是日，得脫一劫餓鬼之苦。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0779c02"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779c0201"><note n="0779036" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔爾時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779036" type="mod">爾時【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779036"><lem wit="【大】">爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>目連復白佛言：「弟子所生<note n="0779037" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔父〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779037" type="mod">父【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779037"><lem wit="【大】">父</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>母，得蒙
<lb ed="T" n="0779c03"/>三寶功德之力、眾僧威神之力。故，若未來世
<lb n="0779c04" ed="T"/>一切佛弟子<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779038" type="orig">〔行孝順者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0779038" type="mod" resp="CBETA">行孝順者【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779038"><lem wit="【大】">行孝順者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，<note n="0779039" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">亦應＝應亦【宋】</note><note n="0779039" type="mod" resp="CBETA">亦應【大】，應亦【宋】</note><app n="0779039"><lem wit="【大】">亦應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">應亦</rdg></app>奉<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779040" type="orig">〔此〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779040" type="mod">此【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779040"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>盂蘭盆，
<lb n="0779c05" ed="T"/>救度現在父母乃至七世父母，為可爾<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779041">不＝否【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0779041" resp="CBETA">不【大】，否【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779041"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">否</rdg></app>？」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0779c06"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779c0601">佛言：「大善快問！我正欲說，汝今復問。善男
<lb ed="T" n="0779c07"/>子！若<note type="orig" n="0779042" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔有〕－【明】</note><note type="mod" n="0779042" resp="CBETA">有【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0779042"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>比丘比丘尼、國王太子、<note n="0779043" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔王子〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779043" type="mod">王子【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779043"><lem wit="【大】">王子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大臣
<lb ed="T" n="0779c08"/>宰相、三公百官、萬民庶人行<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779044" type="orig">孝慈＝慈孝【三】</note><note n="0779044" type="mod" resp="CBETA">孝慈【大】，慈孝【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779044"><lem wit="【大】">孝慈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">慈孝</rdg></app>者，皆<note type="orig" n="0779045" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">應＋（先）【三】</note><note n="0779045" type="mod" resp="CBETA">應【大】，應先【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779045"><lem wit="【大】">應</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">應先</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0779c09"/>為所生現在父母、過去七世父母，於七月十
<lb n="0779c10" ed="T"/>五日——佛歡喜日、僧自恣日——以百味<note n="0779046" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">飲＝飯【元】</note><note n="0779046" type="mod" resp="CBETA">飲【大】，飯【元】</note><app n="0779046"><lem wit="【大】">飲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">飯</rdg></app>食安
<lb n="0779c11" ed="T"/>盂蘭盆中，施十方自恣僧，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779047" type="orig">〔乞〕－【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0779047" resp="CBETA">乞【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779047"><lem wit="【大】">乞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>願<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779048">〔便〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779048">便【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779048"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>使現在
<lb ed="T" n="0779c12"/>父母壽命百年、無病，無一切苦惱之患，乃至
<lb n="0779c13" ed="T"/>七世父母離餓鬼苦，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779049">〔得〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0779049" resp="CBETA">得【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779049"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>生<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779050">天人＝人天【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779050" type="mod">天人【大】，人天【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779050"><lem wit="【大】">天人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">人天</rdg></app>中，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779051" type="orig">福＝富【元】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779051" type="mod">福【大】，富【元】</note><app n="0779051"><lem wit="【大】">福</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">富</rdg></app>樂無
<lb ed="T" n="0779c14"/>極。」</p>
<lb n="0779c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779c1501"><note type="orig" n="0779052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔佛告…人〕九字－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779052" type="mod">（佛告…人）九字【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="9" n="0779052"><lem wit="【大】">佛告諸善男子、善女人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>：「是佛弟子修孝順者，
<lb ed="T" n="0779c16"/>應念念中常憶父母，<note n="0779053" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔供養〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779053">供養【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779053"><lem wit="【大】">供養</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>乃至七世父母。年
<lb n="0779c17" ed="T"/>年七月十五日，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0779054" type="orig">常＝當【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0779054" resp="CBETA">常【大】，當【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779054"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">當</rdg></app>以孝<note type="orig" n="0779055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔順〕－【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0779055" resp="CBETA">順【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0779055"><lem wit="【大】">順</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>慈憶所生父母，
<lb ed="T" n="0779c18"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" n="0779056" type="orig">〔乃至七世父母〕－【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0779056" type="mod">乃至七世父母【大】，〔－〕【元】【明】</note><app n="0779056"><lem wit="【大】">乃至七世父母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，為作盂蘭盆施佛及僧，以報
<lb n="0779c19" ed="T"/>父母長養、慈愛之恩。若一切佛弟子應當奉
<lb ed="T" n="0779c20"/>持是法。」</p>
<lb n="0779c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0779c2101"><app corresp="#0779031" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時目連比丘、四輩弟子，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0779057">〔聞佛所說〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0779057">聞佛所說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0779057"><lem wit="【大】">聞佛所說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，歡喜
<lb n="0779c22" ed="T"/>奉行。</p></cb:div>
